    <item>
      <title>NYCB 因贷款监管薄弱而更换首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/nycb-cites-weakness-in-loan-oversight-replaces-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行任命了一位新首席执行官，并减记了多年前收购的公司的价值，这家商业房地产贷款机构表示，它在跟踪贷款风险的方式上发现了“重大缺陷”。查理·威尔斯在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/nycb-cites-weakness-in-loan-oversight-replaces-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:25:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲期货交易所距离直接清算对冲基金回购交易又近了一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/eurex-moves-closer-to-clearing-hedge-fund-repo-trades-directly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲期货交易所清算公司（Eurex Clearing AG）计划在今年年中之前直接开始为对冲基金进行回购交易清算，这是改善多年来一直受到金融监管收紧限制的市场流动性的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/eurex-moves-closer-to-clearing-hedge-fund-repo-trades-directly</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:21:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦通胀因食品价格大幅下跌而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-on-sharp-decline-in-food-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦2月份通胀连续第二个月放缓，大宗商品价格放缓和食品成本下降有助于抑制物价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-on-sharp-decline-in-food-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票估值与泡沫不一致：高盛的奥本海默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/stock-valuations-not-consistent-with-a-bubble-goldman-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛(Goldman Sachs)首席全球股票策略师彼得·奥本海默(Peter Oppenheimer)表示，股票估值“相当高”，但“反映出基本面相当不错”，因为他认为市场并未出现乐观情绪。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/stock-valuations-not-consistent-with-a-bubble-goldman-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏黎世首席执行官 Greco：人工智能帮助我们更好地理解风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/zurich-ceo-greco-ai-helps-us-understand-risk-better</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏黎世保险首席执行官 Mario Greco 讨论了人工智能如何改变保险业以及苏黎世如何实施该技术。 2 月 28 日，他在彭博社的“The Pulse”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-01/zurich-ceo-greco-ai-helps-us-understand-risk-better</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼集团计划在印度中部邦投资 90 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/adani-group-plans-to-invest-9-billion-in-central-indian-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼集团计划在印度中部中央邦投资超过 7500 亿卢比（90 亿美元），亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 领导的这家企业集团在 2023 年初遭受严厉的卖空攻击后恢复了资本支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/adani-group-plans-to-invest-9-billion-in-central-indian-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金交易员因丹麦税务股息欺诈被判入狱 8 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/hedge-fund-trader-patterson-jailed-for-8-years-over-danish-tax-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金交易员安东尼·帕特森 (Anthony Patterson) 在丹麦承认通过虚假 Cum-Ex 税务交易帮助诈骗国家财政部约 84 亿克朗（12 亿美元），被判处 8 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/hedge-fund-trader-patterson-jailed-for-8-years-over-danish-tax-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理警告称，印尼镍价可能出现赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/nickel-may-flip-to-deficit-on-indonesia-hurdles-macquarie-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司表示，如果印尼产量增长受到采矿许可证审批缓慢的限制，今年全球镍市场可能会意外出现赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/nickel-may-flip-to-deficit-on-indonesia-hurdles-macquarie-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 08:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
